blocks.name: orcomdd
blocks.content: Commutativity of logic disjunction, in double deduction form. Should not be moved to main, see PR #3034 in Github. Use ~ orcomd instead. (Contributed by Giovanni Mascellani, 19-Mar-2018.) (New usage is discouraged.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)

blocks.name: scottexf
blocks.content: A version of ~ scottex with non-free variables instead of distinct variables. (Contributed by Giovanni Mascellani, 19-Aug-2018.)

thm scottexf(setvar s0, setvar s1, class c0) {
  |- wcel(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), universe)
  -| wnfc(s1, c0)
  -| wnfc(s0, c0)
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
} = {
  eqeltri(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), universe, crab(hs0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))))
  eqtr4i(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), crab(hs0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))), crab(s0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))))
  rabbii(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1)))), wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  cbvralf(s1, hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfcv(hs1, c0)
  nfv(hs1, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))
  nfv(s1, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  sseq2d(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)), wceq(cv(s1), cv(hs1)))
  fveq2(cv(s1), cv(hs1), crnk)
  cbvrab(hs0, s0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))), wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  nfcv(hs0, c0)
  nfral(s0, hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfv(s0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfv(hs0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  ralbidv(hs1, c0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  sseq1d(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)), cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), wceq(cv(hs0), cv(s0)))
  fveq2(cv(hs0), cv(s0), crnk)
  scottex(hs0, hs1, c0)
  diff.hs1.c(c0)
  diff.hs1.w(wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))
  diff.wss.s(s1, cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, cv(s0))
  diff.cv.s(s1, s0)
  diffss.ex(s1, s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, cv(hs1))
  diff.crnk.s(s1)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s1)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.wss.s(s0, cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, cv(hs0))
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, cv(hs1))
  diff.crnk.s(s0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.w(wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  diff.hs1.w(wceq(cv(hs0), cv(s0)))
  diff.hs0.s(hs1)
}

thm scottexf(setvar s0, setvar s1, class c0) {
  ‚ä¢ { s0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1))} ‚àà ùïå
  ‚ä£ F/(s1, c0)
  ‚ä£ F/(s0, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s1)
} = {
  eqeltri({ s0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1))}, universe, { hs0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))})
  eqtr4i({ s0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1))}, { hs0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))}, { s0 ‚àà c0 | ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))})
  rabbii(s0, c0, ‚àÄ(s1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1)), ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1)))
  cbvralf(s1, hs1, c0, (rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1), (rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))
  nfcv(hs1, c0)
  nfv(hs1, (rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1))
  nfv(s1, (rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))
  sseq2d((rank ` s0), (rank ` s1), (rank ` hs1), s1 = hs1)
  fveq2(s1, hs1, crnk)
  cbvrab(hs0, s0, c0, ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1)), ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1)))
  nfcv(hs0, c0)
  nfral(s0, hs1, c0, (rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))
  nfv(s0, (rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))
  nfv(hs0, ‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1)))
  ralbidv(hs1, c0, hs0 = s0, (rank ` hs0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1), (rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1))
  sseq1d((rank ` hs0), (rank ` hs1), (rank ` s0), hs0 = s0)
  fveq2(hs0, s0, crnk)
  scottex(hs0, hs1, c0)
  diff.hs1.c(c0)
  diff.hs1.w((rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` s1))
  diff.wss.s(s1, (rank ` s0), (rank ` hs1))
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, s0)
  diff.cv.s(s1, s0)
  diffss.ex(s1, s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, hs1)
  diff.crnk.s(s1)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s1)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.wss.s(s0, (rank ` hs0), (rank ` hs1))
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, hs0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, hs1)
  diff.crnk.s(s0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.w(‚àÄ(hs1 ‚àà c0,(rank ` s0)‚äÜ(rank ` hs1)))
  diff.hs1.w(hs0 = s0)
  diff.hs0.s(hs1)
}

  -| wnfc(s1, c0)
  -| wnfc(s0, c0)
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
} = {
  bitr4i(wceq(c0, emptycls), wceq(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), emptycls), wceq(crab(hs0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))), emptycls))
  scott0(hs0, hs1, c0)
  eqeq1i(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), emptycls, crab(hs0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))))
  eqtr4i(crab(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))), crab(hs0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))), crab(s0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))))
  rabbii(s0, c0, wral(s1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1)))), wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  cbvralf(s1, hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfcv(hs1, c0)
  nfv(hs1, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))
  nfv(s1, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  sseq2d(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)), wceq(cv(s1), cv(hs1)))
  fveq2(cv(s1), cv(hs1), crnk)
  cbvrab(hs0, s0, c0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))), wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  nfcv(hs0, c0)
  nfral(s0, hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfv(s0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  nfv(hs0, wral(hs1, c0, wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))))
  ralbidv(hs1, c0, wceq(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))), wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1))))
  sseq1d(cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)), cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), wceq(cv(hs0), cv(s0)))
  fveq2(cv(hs0), cv(s0), crnk)
  diff.hs0.s(hs1)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs1.c(c0)
  diff.hs1.w(wss(cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(s1))))
  diff.wss.s(s1, cfv(crnk, cv(s0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, cv(s0))
  diff.cv.s(s1, s0)
  diffss.ex(s1, s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s1, crnk, cv(hs1))
  diff.crnk.s(s1)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s1)
  diff.wss.s(s0, cfv(crnk, cv(hs0)), cfv(crnk, cv(hs1)))
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, cv(hs0))
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.cfv.s(s0, crnk, cv(hs1))
  diff.crnk.s(s0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs1)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs1)
  diff.hs1.s(s0)

}

blocks.name: ac6s3f
blocks.content: Generalization of the Axiom of Choice to classes, with bound-variable hypothesis. (Contributed by Giovanni Mascellani, 19-Aug-2018.)
blocks.origin:
thm ac6s3f(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, wff w0, wff w1) {
  |- wi(wral(s0, c0, wex(s1, w0)), wex(s2, wral(s0, c0, w1)))
  -| wnf(s1, w1)
  -| wcel(c0, universe)
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s1), cfv(cv(s2), cv(s0))), wb(w0, w1))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s2, c0)
  -| diffsw(s2, w0)
} = {
  3syl(wral(s0, c0, wex(s1, w0)), wex(s2, wral(s0, c0, w1)), wral(s0, c0, wrex(s1, universe, w0)), wex(s2, wa(wf(cv(s2), c0, universe), wral(s0, c0, w1))))
  biimpri(wral(s0, c0, wex(s1, w0)), wral(s0, c0, wrex(s1, universe, w0)))
  ralbii(s0, c0, wrex(s1, universe, w0), wex(s1, w0))
  rexv(s1, w0)
  ac6sf(s0, s1, s2, c0, universe, w0, w1)
  exsimpr(s2, wf(cv(s2), c0, universe), wral(s0, c0, w1))
  diff.universe.s(s0)
  diff.universe.s(s1)
  diff.universe.s(s2)
}

thm ac6s3f(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, wff w0, wff w1) {
  ‚ä¢ (‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s1, w0))‚Üí ‚àÉ(s2, ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, w1)))
  ‚ä£ F/(s1, w1)
  ‚ä£ c0 ‚àà ùïå
  ‚ä£ (s1 =(s2 ` s0)‚Üí(w0 ‚Üî w1))
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s1)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s1, s2)
  ‚ä£ d(s0, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s2, c0)
  ‚ä£ d(s2, w0)
} = {
  3syl(‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s1, w0)), ‚àÉ(s2, ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, w1)), ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà ùïå, w0)), ‚àÉ(s2,((s2 : c0 ‚Üí ùïå)‚àß ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, w1))))
  biimpri(‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s1, w0)), ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà ùïå, w0)))
  ralbii(s0, c0, ‚àÉ(s1 ‚àà ùïå, w0), ‚àÉ(s1, w0))
  rexv(s1, w0)
  ac6sf(s0, s1, s2, c0, universe, w0, w1)
  exsimpr(s2, (s2 : c0 ‚Üí ùïå), ‚àÄ(s0 ‚àà c0, w1))
  diff.universe.s(s0)
  diff.universe.s(s1)
  diff.universe.s(s2)
}

blocks.name: ac6s6
blocks.content: Generalization of the Axiom of Choice to classes, moving the existence condition in the consequent. (Contributed by Giovanni Mascellani, 19-Aug-2018.)
blocks.origin:
thm ac6s6(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, wff w0, wff w1) {
  |- wex(s0, wral(s1, c0, wi(wex(s2, w0), w1)))
  -| wnf(s2, w1)
  -| wcel(c0, universe)
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s2), cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1))), wb(w0, w1))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s1, c0)
  -| diffsw(s0, w0)
} = {
  ax-mp(wex(s0, wral(s1, c0, wi(wex(s2, w0), w1))), wral(s1, c0, wex(s2, wcel(cv(s2), cif(cab(s2, w0), universe, wex(s2, w0))))))
  rgenw(s1, c0, wex(s2, wcel(cv(s2), cif(cab(s2, w0), universe, wex(s2, w0)))))
  pm2.61i(wex(s2, wcel(cv(s2), cif(cab(s2, w0), universe, wex(s2, w0)))), wex(s2, w0))
  ibir(wex(s2, w0), wex(s2, wcel(cv(s2), cif(cab(s2, w0), universe, wex(s2, w0)))))
  exbidh(s2, wex(s2, w0), wcel(cv(s2), cif(cab(s2, w0), universe, wex(s2, w0))), w0)

blocks.name: ac6s6f
blocks.content: Generalization of the Axiom of Choice to classes, moving the existence condition in the consequent. (Contributed by Giovanni Mascellani, 20-Aug-2018.)
blocks.origin:
thm ac6s6f(setvar s0, setvar s1, setvar s2, class c0, wff w0, wff w1) {
  |- wex(s0, wral(s1, c0, wi(wex(s2, w0), w1)))
  -| wcel(c0, universe)
  -| wnf(s2, w1)
  -| wi(wceq(cv(s2), cfv(cv(s0), cv(s1))), wb(w0, w1))
  -| wnfc(s1, c0)
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s1, s2)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsw(s0, w0)
